 i zanimljivo je

1178
01:33:18,400 --> 01:33:19,460
 kad gledamo Isusa

1179
01:33:19,460 --> 01:33:20,820
 i njegovo odnos sa Otcem,

1180
01:33:20,820 --> 01:33:21,340
 uvek, ono,

1181
01:33:21,340 --> 01:33:22,700
 nebrojno puta o evanđeljima

1182
01:33:22,700 --> 01:33:23,180
 čitamo,

1183
01:33:23,180 --> 01:33:24,980
 Isus se povuče u osamu

1184
01:33:24,980 --> 01:33:26,000
 i ode Isus rano,

1185
01:33:26,000 --> 01:33:27,140
 jutro još za mraka,

1186
01:33:27,140 --> 01:33:28,060
 kako bi molio.

1187
01:33:28,060 --> 01:33:29,280
 Provede noć moja.

1188
01:33:29,280 --> 01:33:30,180
 I provede noć moja,

1189
01:33:30,180 --> 01:33:30,600
 međutim,

1190
01:33:30,600 --> 01:33:31,660
 mi nikad ne znamo

1191
01:33:31,660 --> 01:33:33,120
 kako je to izgledalo.

1192
01:33:33,120 --> 01:33:35,100
 Što bi značilo,

1193
01:33:35,100 --> 01:33:37,100
 Isus nije htio,

1194
01:33:37,100 --> 01:33:39,400
 nije nam htio to pokazati,

1195
01:33:39,400 --> 01:33:40,760
 da ne bi mi toga napravili

1196
01:33:40,760 --> 01:33:41,860
 formu i formulu

1197
01:33:41,860 --> 01:33:43,620
 i tri koraka do uspješne molitve

1198
01:33:43,620 --> 01:33:45,140
 ili pet koraka do nečega.

1199
01:33:45,140 --> 01:33:46,600
 Zato što je to odnos

1200
01:33:46,600 --> 01:33:48,340
 i zašto je tiga da svako osobno

1201
01:33:48,340 --> 01:33:49,760
 ima svoj i svoju vrstu

1202
01:33:49,760 --> 01:33:51,060
 ovaj odnosa.

1203
01:33:51,060 --> 01:33:51,640
 Međutim,

1204
01:33:51,640 --> 01:33:53,100
 postoje neke, naravno,

1205
01:33:53,100 --> 01:33:53,560
 ono,

1206
01:33:53,560 --> 01:33:55,960
 zakonitosti duhovne,

1207
01:33:55,960 --> 01:33:56,660
 a to je ono,

1208
01:33:56,660 --> 01:33:57,460
 prvo pojavi se.

1209
01:33:57,460 --> 01:33:59,480
 Pojavi se

1210
01:33:59,480 --> 01:34:02,460
 koliko god da teško bilo,

1211
01:34:02,460 --> 01:34:03,840
 koliko god da dosadno je bilo,

1212
01:34:03,840 --> 01:34:04,260
 super,

1213
01:34:04,260 --> 01:34:05,580
 koliko god da nemo vremena,

1214
01:34:05,580 --> 01:34:06,240
 pojavi se.

1215
01:34:06,240 --> 01:34:07,920
 Za početak se samo trebaš pojaviti.

1216
01:34:07,920 --> 01:34:10,640
 Znači, samo ustraj i pojavi se

1217
01:34:10,640 --> 01:34:12,520
 i nemoj odustat.

1218
01:34:13,140 --> 01:34:14,480
 Ja bih rekao druga stvar,

1219
01:34:14,480 --> 01:34:16,840
 dođi kakav jesi,

1220
01:34:16,840 --> 01:34:18,120
 to si isto već ti reka,

1221
01:34:18,120 --> 01:34:18,920
 to su već spominjali.

1222
01:34:18,920 --> 01:34:19,340
 Znači,

1223
01:34:19,340 --> 01:34:21,600
 ako ti se ne da molit,

1224
01:34:21,600 --> 01:34:23,100
 i ako misliš da je to glupo,

1225
01:34:23,100 --> 01:34:24,840
 e pa recimo ovo je glupo.

1226
01:34:24,840 --> 01:34:25,800
 Ali ideš molit,

1227
01:34:25,800 --> 01:34:26,780
 ali mu kažeš ne da mi se.

1228
01:34:26,780 --> 01:34:27,500
 Tako je.

1229
01:34:27,500 --> 01:34:28,400
 Znači, to je ono,

1230
01:34:28,400 --> 01:34:29,100
 pojavi se.

1231
01:34:29,100 --> 01:34:30,160
 Drugo,

1232
01:34:30,160 --> 01:34:31,680
 dođi kakav jesi,

1233
01:34:31,680 --> 01:34:33,140
 šta god da imaš,

1234
01:34:33,140 --> 01:34:35,560
 ljud sam na muža,

1235
01:34:35,560 --> 01:34:36,060
 na ženu,

1236
01:34:36,060 --> 01:34:36,800
 na posao,

1237
01:34:36,800 --> 01:34:37,940
 na tebe Bože,

1238
01:34:37,940 --> 01:34:38,840
 šta god da imaš,

1239
01:34:38,840 --> 01:34:39,500
 dođi s tim

1240
01:34:39,500 --> 01:34:41,020
 i to mu daje.

1241
01:34:41,020 --> 01:34:43,140
 To je broj dva.

1242
01:34:43,140 --> 01:34:47,300
 I rekao bi broj tri,

1243
01:34:47,300 --> 01:34:49,040
 možda ono,

1244
01:34:49,040 --> 01:34:51,420
 već kad ovo dvoje savladaš,

1245
01:34:51,420 --> 01:34:53,080
 ono kad već nekako to dođe,

1246
01:34:53,080 --> 01:34:54,440
 broj tri bi rekao,

1247
01:34:54,440 --> 01:34:56,080
 moramo bit,

1248
01:34:56,080 --> 01:34:57,240
 ne znam kada to je lijepo,

1249
01:34:57,240 --> 01:34:57,520
 kažemo,

1250
01:34:57,600 --> 01:34:58,340
 nekako kratko,

1251
01:34:58,340 --> 01:35:01,940
 ali molitva mora bit vođena

1252
01:35:01,940 --> 01:35:02,800
 Duhom Svetim.

1253
01:35:02,800 --> 01:35:03,880
 Znači,

1254
01:35:03,880 --> 01:35:06,280
 svaka molitva se temelji

1255
01:35:06,280 --> 01:35:07,200
 na odnosu

1256
01:35:07,200 --> 01:35:08,080
 i mora bit vođena

1257
01:35:08,080 --> 01:35:08,880
 Duhom Svetim.

1258
01:35:08,880 --> 01:35:11,620
 Zato nema forme,

1259
01:35:11,620 --> 01:35:13,500
 zato ne možeš znat kako,

1260
01:35:13,500 --> 01:35:14,580
 mora bit vođena

1261
01:35:14,580 --> 01:35:15,800
 Duhom Svetim

1262
01:35:15,800 --> 01:35:16,640
 i to je ono,

1263
01:35:16,640 --> 01:35:17,220
 doslovno,

1264
01:35:17,220 --> 01:35:18,500
 znači onda bih rekao,

1265
01:35:18,500 --> 01:35:19,300
 ajde treći korak,

1266
01:35:19,300 --> 01:35:19,940
 pite ga Bože,

1267
01:35:19,940 --> 01:35:21,500
 što ti danas želiš.

1268
01:35:21,500 --> 01:35:23,180
 Hvala lijepo kad si konkretno.

1269
01:35:23,180 --> 01:35:24,380
 Ne, ozbjeno.

1270
01:35:24,380 --> 01:35:26,880
 Ne, odlično si stvarno,

1271
01:35:26,880 --> 01:35:28,560
 rekao,

1272
01:35:28,560 --> 01:35:30,220
 ne znam uopće što bih dodala,

1273
01:35:30,220 --> 01:35:32,660
 jedino bih dodala možda,

1274
01:35:32,660 --> 01:35:36,680
 mi ne znam uopće

1275
01:35:36,680 --> 01:35:38,280
 koliko naša molitva vrijedi,

1276
01:35:38,280 --> 01:35:39,000
 odnosno,

1277
01:35:39,000 --> 01:35:41,060
 mi često imamo tu tendenciju

1278
01:35:41,060 --> 01:35:42,600
 gledati kroz ljudske oči

1279
01:35:42,600 --> 01:35:45,040
 i zato ovo što kažeš,

1280
01:35:45,040 --> 01:35:46,660
 možda je vrijednije baš to,

1281
01:35:46,660 --> 01:35:48,020
 da se ti pojaviš,

1282
01:35:48,020 --> 01:35:50,220
 izdvojiš svoje vrijeme

1283
01:35:50,220 --> 01:35:52,260
 i ono,

1284
01:35:52,260 --> 01:35:53,140
 mučiš se,

1285
01:35:53,140 --> 01:35:55,600
 možda se mučiš tri mjeseca

1286
01:35:55,600 --> 01:35:56,980
 i uvijek isto,

1287
01:35:56,980 --> 01:35:58,180
 i uvijek isti ishod,

1288
01:35:58,180 --> 01:36:00,500
 ali ti ne znaš šta se događa

1289
01:36:00,500 --> 01:36:03,580
 i koje milosti i blagoslove otvaraš

1290
01:36:03,580 --> 01:36:04,320
 u svom srcu,

1291
01:36:04,320 --> 01:36:07,160
 u svom životu za veći prodor milosti.

1292
01:36:07,160 --> 01:36:08,480
 Ti jednostavno ne znaš

1293
01:36:08,480 --> 01:36:11,260
 i ne trebaš ulaziti u odnos sa računicom

1294
01:36:11,260 --> 01:36:13,280
 da da mučiš ću se tako da dobijem ne,

1295
01:36:13,280 --> 01:36:15,900
 nego ulaziš u odnos zbog odnosa,

1296
01:36:15,900 --> 01:36:16,540
 zbog njega.

1297
01:36:16,540 --> 01:36:19,380
 Dakle, htjela bih samo to reći,

1298
01:36:19,380 --> 01:36:21,860
 da nipošto se ne stavlja

1299
01:36:21,860 --> 01:36:24,820
 i u to neke opipljive okvire,

1300
01:36:24,820 --> 01:36:26,720
 jer mi ne znamo,

1301
01:36:26,720 --> 01:36:31,040
 koliko može biti vrijedniji taj naš napor

1302
01:36:31,040 --> 01:36:34,020
 da odvojim vrijeme,

1303
01:36:34,020 --> 01:36:35,560
 iako mi je teško,

1304
01:36:35,560 --> 01:36:37,000
 iako ništa ne osjećam,

1305
01:36:37,000 --> 01:36:38,940
 kako Bog na to gleda.

1306
01:36:38,940 --> 01:36:42,300
 Ja vjerujem da Bog na to gleda

1307
01:36:42,300 --> 01:36:44,260
 s velikim ponosom

1308
01:36:44,260 --> 01:36:47,920
 i da se milost probija ogromno,

1309
01:36:47,920 --> 01:36:49,160
 ogromno na tvoj život.

1310
01:36:49,160 --> 01:36:50,680
 Bravo.

1311
01:36:50,680 --> 01:36:53,840
 Da, hvala vam.

1312
01:36:53,840 --> 01:36:55,140
 Ne znam kaj bih rekao drugo.

1313
01:36:55,140 --> 01:36:57,400
 Vrš vam hvala.

1314
01:36:57,400 --> 01:37:00,440
 Hvala na neki način

1315
01:37:00,440 --> 01:37:01,560
 i za sve kaj ste prošli

1316
01:37:01,560 --> 01:37:03,320
 sami u odnosu s Bogom,

1317
01:37:03,320 --> 01:37:05,180
 pa sad mi to možemo

1318
01:37:05,180 --> 01:37:06,800
 naučiti nekaj od vas,

1319
01:37:06,800 --> 01:37:08,940
 a da nije da moramo sami prolaziti.

1320
01:37:08,940 --> 01:37:10,880
 Hvala vam kaj ste odvojili vrijeme,

1321
01:37:10,880 --> 01:37:11,860
 kaj ste tu došli

1322
01:37:11,860 --> 01:37:14,420
 i sa mnom ste se rado odazvali.

1323
01:37:14,420 --> 01:37:15,260
 Ja to znam,

1324
01:37:15,260 --> 01:37:17,260
 tako da, evo,

1325
01:37:17,260 --> 01:37:18,620
 baš vas je bilo blagoslovo imati.

1326
01:37:18,620 --> 01:37:21,120
 Dragi naši prijatelji,

1327
01:37:21,120 --> 01:37:22,740
 prije nego što odjavimo

1328
01:37:22,740 --> 01:37:23,940
 ovu emisiju,

1329
01:37:23,940 --> 01:37:26,240
 kao što ste već čuli dva puta,

1330
01:37:26,240 --> 01:37:28,800
 Matej je napisao knjigu

1331
01:37:28,800 --> 01:37:30,340
 Zove Sjeda na jedan sa Bogom.

1332
01:37:30,340 --> 01:37:33,460
 može se kupiti putem web shopa

1333
01:37:33,460 --> 01:37:34,420
 naše zajednice.

1334
01:37:34,420 --> 01:37:37,780
 Ja znam puno ljudi

1335
01:37:37,780 --> 01:37:39,500
 koji ju imaju.

1336
01:37:39,500 --> 01:37:41,040
 Ja sam sve veri,

1337
01:37:41,040 --> 01:37:42,000
 imamo dva primjerka

1338
01:37:42,000 --> 01:37:42,600
 i evo, stvarno,

1339
01:37:42,600 --> 01:37:43,540
 svima je preporučamo.

1340
01:37:43,540 --> 01:37:45,080
 Dakle, možete ne baviti

1341
01:37:45,080 --> 01:37:47,080
 preko web shopa Bože pobjede.

1342
01:37:47,080 --> 01:37:49,740
 I druga vrlo važna stvar je,

1343
01:37:49,740 --> 01:37:51,360
 vjerojatno ste već čuli

1344
01:37:51,360 --> 01:37:53,100
 ako ste pratili naše društvene mreže,

1345
01:37:53,260 --> 01:37:55,240
 a to je da naša zajednica

1346
01:37:55,240 --> 01:37:56,380
 organizira večer slavljenja

1347
01:37:56,380 --> 01:37:58,260
 slavljenja ovoga puta

1348
01:37:58,260 --> 01:37:59,420
 na jugu,

1349
01:37:59,420 --> 01:38:00,200
 u Splitu,

1350
01:38:00,200 --> 01:38:02,200
 14. listopada

1351
01:38:02,200 --> 01:38:03,500
 u dvorani Gripe.

1352
01:38:03,500 --> 01:38:06,000
 Ko nije kupio kartu,

1353
01:38:06,000 --> 01:38:08,180
 stigne još kratko koliko ih ima

1354
01:38:08,180 --> 01:38:09,780
 i nadam se da se vidimo.

1355
01:38:09,780 --> 01:38:11,420
 Svi ćemo biti tamo.

1356
01:38:12,700 --> 01:38:13,460
 Ako neko neće,

1357
01:38:13,460 --> 01:38:14,120
 vjerojatno sad neće

1358
01:38:14,120 --> 01:38:15,060
 to nisi reći,

1359
01:38:15,060 --> 01:38:16,260
 ali svi ćemo biti tamo.

1360
01:38:16,260 --> 01:38:17,360
 Tak da evo,

1361
01:38:17,360 --> 01:38:18,960
 vidimo svijedući mjesec.

1362
01:38:18,960 --> 01:38:21,260
 Pratite sve naše sadržaje

1363
01:38:21,260 --> 01:38:23,280
 na našim društvenim mrežama

1364
01:38:23,280 --> 01:38:24,340
 i vidimo se.

1365
01:38:24,340 --> 01:38:25,060
 Hvala na gledanju.

1366
01:38:25,060 --> 01:38:25,280
 Bok!

1367
01:38:25,280 --> 01:38:25,840
 Bok!

1368
01:38:25,840 --> 01:38:26,380
 Tako!

1369
01:38:26,380 --> 01:38:28,380
 Bok!

